declarations.description: Code widget for HTML with live preview functionality.
declarations.name: CodeHTML

attributes.name: code
attributes.description: The source code content displayed in the editor.

attributes.name: visible
attributes.description: Whether the code editor is visible to the user.

attributes.name: autoRun
attributes.description: Whether to automatically run the code when the component is first loaded.

attributes.name: runnable
attributes.description: Whether the code execution is allowed and the run button is enabled.

attributes.name: autocomplete
attributes.description: Whether autocompletion is enabled in the code editor.

attributes.name: lockedLines
attributes.description: Array of line numbers that should be locked from editing.

attributes.name: showExecutionTime
attributes.description: Whether to display the execution time in the controls.

attributes.name: executionTime
attributes.description: The execution time in milliseconds of the last code run.

attributes.name: showExecutionCount
attributes.description: Whether to display the execution count in the run button.

attributes.name: executionCount
attributes.description: The number of times the code has been executed.

attributes.name: results
attributes.description: The results from the last code execution.

attributes.name: diagnostics
attributes.description: Compilation or runtime errors from the last code execution.
